部队进入[[拉塔基亚|拉塔基亚]]，其中有20辆坦克和装甲车。根据活动家所说，那里至少有两个平民被杀。在代尔祖尔，活动家说一名孩子被狙击手射杀<ref>{{cite news|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/08/2011813103322136544.html|date=13 August 2011|accessdate=13 August 2011|agency=Al Jazeera English|title=Syrian army 'enters western coastal city'|archive-date=2013-03-24|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6FLdg0X43?url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2011/08/2011813103322136544.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一家土耳其报纸《Hürriyet Daily News》报道说，一名匿名的土耳其政府高官表示在土耳其的领导下军事干预叙利亚是一种可行的方式。该报道暗示土耳其政府对该地区教派紧张形势的严重焦虑，因为叙利亚局势已经影响到了[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]边界地区的不稳定<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/n.php?n=syria-intervention-not-off-table-2011-08-12#.TkaR7iNMDA8.blogger|agency=Hürriyet Daily News|title=Syria intervention not off table|first=Murat|last=Yetkin|date=13 August 2011|accessdate=13 August 2011|archive-date=2011-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111117123830/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/n.php?n=syria-intervention-not-off-table-2011-08-12#.TkaR7iNMDA8.blogger|dead-url=no}}</ref>。LCC报道说，在[[古賽爾_(敘利亞)|古賽爾]]、[[德拉雅|德拉雅]]和[[哈马|哈马]]各有1人死亡<ref>{{cite news|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/08/2011813204032987391.html|agency=Al Jazeera English|title=Deaths reported in Syria military assaults|date=13 August 2011|accessdate=13 August 2011|archive-date=2018-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180801140246/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2011/08/2011813204032987391.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

